SUMMARY:Feel the burn folks on this Bike Ride led by ITALO!
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\n**MEETUP POINT: Woodbine Park
  in front of the Beach Club - 1681 Lake Shore Blvd E**\nJoin us for a 50km
  bike ride in the city. Don't worry it's flat! Led by Italo who is an expe
 rienced cyclist and leader\, so you will be in good hands. It's lots of fu
 n and not too far!\nThe ride begins at Woodbine park and ends nearby for a
  social and lunch. (I'll keep you posted on where it will be.)\nPlease com
 e prepared with the right riding gear which means not a commuter bike.\nTh
 is wouldn't be a beginner bike ride.\nBring lots of water and snacks.\nHel
 mets obviously a must!\n[https://ridewithgps.com/routes/53737876](https://
 ridewithgps.com/routes/53737876)
