BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: These Boots Are Made for Hiking
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/these-boots-are-made-for-hiking/
UID:event_313240228@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260325T025240Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260711T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260718T213000
SUMMARY:Mangiare\, Hike\, Repeat 
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\n**Ciao Bella!** For our first
  international trip of the year - we have are heading to ITALY to trekk th
 e dolomites or hike and tour Italy.\n**JULY 11 - July 19**\nThis works in 
 two ways - 2 groups\, 2 paths. Because not everyone wants to trekk for fou
 r days\, and because we are a large group we always offer two ways to come
  with us\, because well we just want you to experience the best trips and 
 a lot of fun!\n\nSO.....\n1\\. You can sign up for the Trekking portion \\
 - 4 days\\\, 3 nights\\\, hut to hut on the full Val Di Fassa trail plus t
 wo day hikes on the Thursday and Friday in the dolomite region hiking\nOR\
 n2\\. A 7 day tour where we experience day hikes\\\, and Italy's dolomite 
 village life\\. We will spending our time in the Dolomites and Venice for 
 the 7 days enjoying day hikes and hitting iconic dolomite spots along with
  Venice night life and mountain night life\\. We will have lunch at the re
 fugio and either the beginning or the end we will hike with the trecking g
 roup\\.\n\nAll details\, such as the costs\, itinerary\, exact fly in and 
 out cities and meetup points will be supplied in the zoom call below. From
  there those who commit to the trip are then moved to a whats app where we
  follow the nitty gritty details of everyones flight bookings\, gear\, and
  flag ongoing questions\, and ensure you are well prepared and organized f
 or this trip)\n\nIf you miss the zoom call you miss the trip.\n**ZOOM CALL
 : January 28\, 7:30 PM**\n**Meeting ID: 922 573 6911**\n**Passcode: crCjL3
 **\n**https://us05web.zoom.us/j/9225736911?pwd=QW5DamFQV0c5VDJjSis0eGxQZEk
 4QT09&omn=84536132265**\n**Join instructions**\n**https://us05web.zoom.us/
 meetings/84536132265/invitations?signature=ZguA6WuO-K4lE9JeXuA_-M5pdYFisBO
 0dsUEwTmDNgo**
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/these-boots-are-made-for-hiking/event
 s/313240228/
